Comment: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:55.07,Ristorante,Sign,0,0,0,,Paradiso
Comment: 0,0:20:47.72,0:21:01.03,Ristorante,,0,0,0,,casetta dell'orso
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:11.90,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I had fun last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:16.95,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,When can I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:20.91,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Why aren’t you\Nsaying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:25.08,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Would you look\Nme in the eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:29.96,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,How long are you\Ngoing to wear that ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:34.76,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I get it. You still have\Nfeelings for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:41.64,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You said all those nice\Nthings to me. It’s not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:44.35,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You invited {\i1}me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:49.77,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Now hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:00.62,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We’ll be awaiting\Nyour next visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:02.66,Ristorante,MV+FV,0,0,0,,Buona notte.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:04.37,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Buona notte.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.63,0:01:18.30,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,This mysterious restaurant is on a road just a little ways from the center of Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:44.93,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Well? Gotten used to\Nthe restaurant yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:49.39,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Absolutely. I mean, Vito, Luciano,\Nand all of you have been so kind to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.60,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Furio! Teo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:55.57,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Not often I see you with a young lady in tow. A new staff member?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:58.86,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,This is Nicoletta.\NShe’s apprenticing with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.32,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:02.95,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Likewise. And I appreciate\Nyour patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.53,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,This is Mauro.\NHe owns this stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:09.71,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I always try to come here when we need vegetables, in between deliveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.75,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He’s always got some\Nunique things for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:12.79,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.42,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Have any puntarelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.84,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We been sold out for hours. What time do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:20.13,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sheesh, I was just asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.47,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Hey, I told you\Nnot to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:30.98,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Say, do you have\Na girlfriend, Teo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:35.27,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Depends who’s\Nasking, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.61,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.44,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He’s just shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:47.58,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Must be nice…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:59.71,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That daughter of mine… Looks like she’s got a crush on Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.88,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:07.10,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,The one with the red hair, right? I saw her at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:11.89,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But I’m not surprised to hear she did, considering she’s {\i1}your{\i0} daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:12.89,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:16.73,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,A good friend of mine’s daughter.\NI treat her like my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:18.48,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.74,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Oh, I think I heard about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:22.78,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:27.49,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I was talking to Claudio about his wedding ring and when he’s gonna take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:29.41,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She may have gotten\Nthe wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:33.41,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,There’s nothing wrong\Nabout it, Gabrielle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:37.13,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Did he say he’s still\Nin love with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.50,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That’s decidedly\Nuntrue, Olga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.17,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He may have had feelings for me when we broke up,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:46.80,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,but now it’s only because he missed his chance to lose the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.55,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Now he’s stuck in\Na holding pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:52.68,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Olga, you’ve got a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.85,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Your afternoon schedule\Nis packed, so please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.31,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:01.82,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Anyway, let her be.\NIt’ll do her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:05.15,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She still has lots to learn…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:06.82,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Another divorce case today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.58,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I’m so sick of them…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.83,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Why do relationships\Nhave to be so complicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.25,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Olga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:15.50,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:19.08,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It’s tough to be\Na sought-after attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.50,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Season the vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.38,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,But don’t put so much in as to taint the color of the ravioli.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:29.22,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We’re going to serve this as the staff meal, but do you want to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.35,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,She seems a bit\Ndown today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:46.28,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.53,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,She’s depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.83,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Uh, wait, Luciano?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:59.46,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It’s because Gabrielle\Ncame by, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:04.17,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Even if she’s your {\i1}ex-{\i0}wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:09.05,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I know it bothers her. Everyone knows she started working here because she has a thing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:12.97,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It’s all fine and dandy if you want to date a young girl like Vito does,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:18.23,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,but if you don’t,\Nstop being so kind to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.85,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Don’t get her hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.40,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Tonight was another\Nsplendid dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.36,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Here’s a little token\Nof my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:32.16,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.54,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I can’t make it next week,\Nunfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:37.83,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I finally got tickets to the opera in Milan, so I’ll be going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:40.37,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, Santa Lucia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:47.01,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Table five is ready\Nfor their primo course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.09,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:56.10,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Maybe it’s my imagination, but he’s been avoiding looking at me since that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.06,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Nicoletta, stop daydreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.10,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.78,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Night, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:16.37,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It’s my treat. Let’s have a glass of wine at the enoteca.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:19.20,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have\Nsomething to get to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.91,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:24.17,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’ll take a rain check.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:29.97,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Is he avoiding me after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:36.56,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,That’s quite the bargain, Gigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.60,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,What do you say,\Na hundred Euro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:42.35,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You’re breaking\Nmy balls, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.73,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Guess it’s a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:49.44,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’ve been looking\Nfor this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:52.78,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What? Your wife is\Nreally that young, Vito?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:55.41,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Yes, she’s still in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:56.58,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:59.24,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I met her at my old gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:01.87,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I was the one who\Napproached her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.88,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,A couple of exercise\Nfreaks, those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:08.17,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Be careful when you’re with him,\Nunless you like muscle pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:11.17,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,So, what’s it like being married to someone so much younger than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:13.55,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I don’t really think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.93,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Every day is a lot\Nof fun, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:17.80,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You don’t say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:25.48,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Say, Vito… Claudio’s ex—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.98,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.86,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Angela, you’re late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.28,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Who’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.78,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Furio’s wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.11,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,That’s her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.00,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You’re Nicoletta, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.12,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,My husband told\Nme about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:46.96,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I’m Angela.\NPleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:49.25,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,O-Oh, likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:54.63,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,So, how’s the wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.30,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:01.52,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Yes, I think\NI’ll have the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:02.68,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.98,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,This is my lovely bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.57,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.91,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Everyone looks so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:31.84,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Good night. I’ll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.06,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:52.98,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,{Ouch. }Long day at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.86,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Yeah, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:57.07,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I had dinner with a couple\Nwho are a client of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:58.41,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,My shoulders\Nare all stiff now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:02.16,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Say, want to have\Na glass of wine over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:04.08,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Maybe next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:08.67,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I’ll swing by the restaurant\Nsometime then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.71,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Ciao.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.22,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You’re late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:27.14,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Where the heck were\Nyou off gallivanting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:29.31,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Delinquent girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.55,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What’s with\Nall these clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:58.55,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,They’re all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:00.84,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You {\i1}just{\i0} bought\Nme some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.22,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I was out shopping\Nand couldn’t resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.72,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What about work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:06.97,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,My afternoon was free,\Nwhat can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.18,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Okay, I’ll go put some tea on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.91,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You met Gabrielle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:32.92,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.29,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She’s a close friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:42.63,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I told you to lay off Claudio,\Nright? About that…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:48.60,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I won’t say anything\Nif you’re serious about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.44,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.11,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You’re welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:03.78,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,So? Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:17.67,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I can’t tell if my\Nfeelings are real or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:22.59,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But I do think…\NYeah, he’s special.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:27.93,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I’m happy when\Nhe’s around,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.51,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,and I can’t take\Nmy eyes off him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.27,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That’s love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:37.90,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Your mind is filled with\Nthoughts of him. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.82,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That’s the most\Nexciting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:46.24,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You’ve got the real thing,\Nso be confident about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.45,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:53.91,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,As your mother, I should be telling you to date someone your own age.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:57.96,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,However, as a fellow woman,\NI want to say that love knows no age.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:03.26,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But Claudio’s a tough one,\Nso I don’t think it’ll be easy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:12.10,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,The other night, I thought that maybe he still has feelings for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.98,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Yeah, that might be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:20.07,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But he just wears that ring\Nto keep the customers at bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:24.57,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Hey, what was it like when you fell in love with the owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:27.16,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:28.41,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:32.49,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Was he really slender\Nand intelligent-looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:36.33,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Nope. He hasn’t\Nchanged a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:41.67,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He looked like a bear. I fell in love the first time I laid eyes on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.59,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Was he wearing glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.22,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He’s got 20/20 vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:52.10,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Don’t you have\Na spectacles-fetish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:53.93,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:59.27,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,So when he was\Nopening the restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:03.40,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I made him promise to have all the employees wear spectacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:06.07,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Isn’t he such a sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:14.62,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I screwed up once, so I vowed not to fall in love,\Nand tried to focus exclusively on work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.75,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But once I fall for\Nsomeone, I’m hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.50,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I fall head over heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:23.42,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He proposed to me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:29.22,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But he was dead set on not marrying a woman with a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:33.18,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That’s why I had to\Nkeep you a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.31,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:37.14,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He scared me the\Nother day, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:42.56,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He’s got a pretty keen\Nsense of intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.57,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Looking at her…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:54.58,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,I’m envious, and I feel\Nkinda depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:05.46,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Let’s see…\NPorro and broccoli…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:11.84,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You opened another\Nexpensive bottle of wine, Gigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:14.89,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Every day. Because the\Nowner doesn’t notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:17.72,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Hey, I’m not gonna complain about being able to drink good wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:20.02,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:21.39,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:24.36,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Good food calls\Nfor good wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.88,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Dinner’s ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.51,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,A-Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.39,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’ll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:05.69,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Just let me know if\Nanything’s bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:10.19,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I know this might seem\Nstrange of me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:17.66,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Umm, you’ve been acting a little odd ever since Gabrielle stopped by.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:22.08,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, but that’s not what\NI was thinking about right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.21,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:28.13,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Claudio, you don’t have to go out of your way to be nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:31.42,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I overstepped\Nmy boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.59,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Luciano said\Nthe same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.47,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That I’m bothering you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:43.94,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,No, just that it’s rude to be kind to you if it’s not genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.69,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,So what were\Nyou thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:55.66,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That I’m jealous\Nof the owner’s wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.41,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,As a fellow woman, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:17:01.45,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She’s got both her work-life and love-life under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.41,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Everyone here likes her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:10.46,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I think you’ve got a lot in common with her, though…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:16.22,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You’re both straightforward and empowered. But also…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.10,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She’s my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:24.98,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.35,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:27.65,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Keep that a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:33.19,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,The owner\Ndoesn’t know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:36.45,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I actually planned on telling him when I came here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:40.53,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She dumped me at my grandmother’s\Nwhen I was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:43.54,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She never cared\Nfor me much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:49.08,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,And it was all so she\Ncould marry the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:57.01,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But, it’s also because\Nshe got busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:03.01,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I get the fact that her work kept her from caring for me until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:10.52,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,On the other hand, it pisses me off.\NForcing me into this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:15.15,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I feel both jealous\Nof her full lifestyle
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:17.03,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,and even more pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:21.78,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,My ex-wife works in\Nthe same office as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:23.83,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:31.67,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,She got busy with work\Nas well and we were fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:33.88,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,And that’s why\Nyou split up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:37.72,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We tried to talk about it\Nand ended up divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:44.01,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We’ve got a lot\Nin common, us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.72,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,In that we were\Nboth cast aside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:52.69,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:59.53,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Back when we were still together, I could tell from the look on her face how full her life was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:04.24,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Seeing her like that made\Nme feel a little uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:10.17,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,If you ever have any questions,\Njust let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:13.13,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’m not sure how much I can bring to the conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.88,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,but if you ever need\Nsomeone to vent to…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:18.76,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You’re such a\Nnice guy, Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.93,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Are you like\Nthis to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:25.01,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,In the spirit of\Nfull disclosure…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:29.18,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,My real name is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:35.82,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Santo Claudio Paradiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:38.32,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Paradiso?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:10.23,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Santo Claudio Paradiso…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:15.61,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Yes. As a child, I was often\Nmade fun of because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:20.94,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,No, it means “heaven”! What better name could you ask for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:25.91,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You can talk to me\Nwhenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.12,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:43.47,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,He really does\Nseem like a saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:49.68,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You work too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:55.48,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,After you’re discharged tomorrow,\Nwant to stop for a drink on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:59.02,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You know, at the place\Nwhere he works.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:01.03,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Sure.